Package edu.biu.scapi.interactiveMidProtocols.ot.fullSimulation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OTFullSimDDHOnByteArrayReceiver
    Concrete implementation of the receiver side in oblivious transfer based on the DDH assumption that achieves full simulation.
    OTFullSimDDHOnByteArraySender
    Concrete implementation of the sender side in oblivious transfer based on the DDH assumption that achieves full simulation.
    OTFullSimDDHOnGroupElementReceiver
    Concrete implementation of the receiver side in oblivious transfer based on the DDH assumption that achieves full simulation.
    OTFullSimDDHOnGroupElementSender
    Concrete implementation of the sender side in oblivious transfer based on the DDH assumption that achieves full simulation.
    OTFullSimOnByteArrayReceiverTransferUtil
    This class executes the computations in the transfer function that related to the byte[] inputs.
    OTFullSimOnByteArraySenderTransferUtil
    This class executes the computations in the transfer function that related to the byte[] inputs.
    OTFullSimOnGroupElementReceiverTransferUtil
    This class executes the computations in the transfer function that related to the GroupElement inputs.
    OTFullSimOnGroupElementSenderTransferUtil
    This class executes the computations in the transfer function that related to the GroupElement inputs.
    OTFullSimPreprocessPhaseValues
    This class holds the Group Elements calculated in the preprocess phase.
    OTFullSimReceiverPreprocessUtil
    This class execute the preprocess phase of OT's that achieve full simulation.
    OTFullSimReceiverTransferUtilAbs
    This class execute the common functionality of the transfer function of all OT's that achieve full simulation.
    OTFullSimSenderPreprocessUtil
    This class execute the preprocess phase of OT's that achieve full simulation.
    OTFullSimSenderTransferUtilAbs
    This class execute the common functionality of the transfer function of all OT's that achieve full simulation.
